creator: Free crypto and bitcoin signals
descriptionHtml:
Fortune traders - free crypto signals and smart bot provide you signal by experienced persons from cryptocurrencies market and notify you on the best time to buy alts and btc for max profit.

The app will save your time by giving specific and researched deals, that will eventually help you to bypass guessing flaws.

The app will provide with trade list and profit ladders to help you earn money through cryptocurrencies.

Our signals have a very high win rate, our service is one of the best.

With our signals you can choose between 4 targets with options of

1) Target 1 and 2 is Day trade,

2) Target 3 and 4 is Swing trade and Hold,

Thus being able to obtain profits in your investments in which strategy you prefer.

Bitcoin trading was never easier, when our app will find the trend and provide you trading signals. This app provides data from BINANCE cryptocurrency exchange, including following symbols: BTCUSD, LTCUSD, ETHUSD, XRPUSD, EOSUSD, DASHUSD, LTCBTC, ETHBTC, BTCEUR, BTCGBP, ETHEUR, BCHUSD, LTCEUR and more.

It sends buy and sell signals of Bitcoin, Ethereum, Litecoin and over 8,000 altcoins with daily notification

To make sure that the signals work, first open positions for small amounts of money. As you increase your profit, you can also increase the volume of transactions. Always use stop-loss!

Download the APP and check out our results that have already been released.

KEY FEATURES

TRADING SIGNALS - LIVE CRYPTO SIGNALS
Our app signals are a perfect way of getting bitcoin market movement tips online. Our crypto signals for trading are based on analyzing many technical indicators. Fortune traders app provides data for Binance currently.

LIVE PUSH NOTIFICATIONS
Stay tuned with the actual prices and market trends. Receive push notification to get the crypto trading signals on time and maximize profit from your transactions.

MORE COIN PAIRS
In the latest update we have added Polkadot (DOT) to the app. Cardano (ADA), Ripple (XRP), Litecoin (LTC), Solana (SOL) and some others also have been added in the latest update. Tell us the pairs you would like to see in the app.

MORE SENSITIVITY
We will constantly improve our trading algorithm, increase the number of indicators to be considered. Also we will tune the sensitivity of the algorithm.

ROADMAP

RISK MANAGEMENT
Want to close positions on time? Always use take profit and stop loss on your orders while entering the position. It will hedge your risks from market fluctuations.

MARKET BOT
Automatically place orders, add your crypto exchange with API. We are hard working on the next update with grid bots, auto-balancing portfolio and many more features!

What coin pairs you want see next in the app next? Leave your reviews about app and its features or contact via email, tell us what you would like to see in the app and we will add these features in future updates.

Please reach out to us at Bitcoinsignals42@gmail.com for any queries

DISCLAIMER: While trading in Cryptocurrency is potentially rewarding, there are alternative risks associated with it. Hence, one should be aware of the possible dangers and ready to accept them in their quest to invest in cryptocurrencies. It is thus not advisable to trade with money you cannot afford to lose. This is not a prompt to trade in cryptocurrencies, and it is not guaranteed that any given account will attain loses or profits. The important thing is that past failure or success is not necessarily an indication of upcoming results.
